Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.610 --> 00:00:04.040
Birgalikda breakpoint ni increment 
metodiga qo‘shishni hamda ushbu 

00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:06.270
 breakpoint ni ishga tushirishni 
ko‘rib chiqamiz.

00:00:06.270 --> 00:00:09.360
Umid qilamanki, siz buni 
kompyuteringizda amalga oshira olasiz.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:11.930
 Decrement metodi uchun, 
agar breakpoint ni 

00:00:11.930 --> 00:00:15.510
qo‘shmoqchi bo‘lsak, 
33-qatorga bosamiz.

00:00:15.510 --> 00:00:19.850
Keyin ilovani debug rejimida ishga 
tushirish uchun ushbu green bug icon ni bosing.

00:00:19.850 --> 00:00:21.740
Men Waiting For Debugger 
xabarini ko‘raman 

00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:23.150
va u tezda yo‘qoladi.

00:00:24.510 --> 00:00:27.200
Ushbu breakpoint ni ishga tushirish uchun 
minus tugmasini bosaman.

00:00:29.110 --> 00:00:30.600
Ilova ushbu qatorda to‘xtab qoladi,

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:33.480
chunki miqdor
qiymati hali yangilanmagan.

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:36.730
Men bu yerda o‘zgaruvchilar 
ro‘yxatini ko‘rmoqdaman, 

00:00:36.730 --> 00:00:39.420
ammo miqdor o‘zgaruvchisi
hali ko‘ringani yo‘q.

00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:42.970
Keyingi qatorga o‘tish uchun ushbu 
qatordan o‘tib tugmani bosaman.

00:00:42.970 --> 00:00:46.990
Keyin miqdor o‘zgaruvchisi ko‘rsatilishini 
ko‘raman, hozirgi qiymati bir.

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.740
So‘ngra, metodning oxiriga qadar kodning 
ushbu qatoridan o‘taman

00:00:50.740 --> 00:00:52.750
va shunchaki ilovani davom ettiraman.

00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:57.420
Ilovada ikki breakpoint mavjud bo‘lganligi 
sababli, agar plyus tugmasini bossam, 

00:00:57.420 --> 00:01:00.060
u increment metodida 
 breakpoint ni chaqiradi.

00:01:00.060 --> 00:01:02.430
Keyin davom ettirish uchun 
 play tugmasini bosaman.

00:01:02.430 --> 00:01:05.470
Agar minus tugmasini bossam,
bu decrement metodida 
 breakpoint ni chaqiradi 

00:01:05.470 --> 00:01:07.970
va men davom etish uchun 
 play tugmasini bosaman.

00:01:07.970 --> 00:01:10.340
Agar men ushbu ilovaning breakpoint larni 
birortasini to‘xtashini xohlamasam, 

00:01:10.340 --> 00:01:13.390
men shunchaki Stop tugmasini bosaman 
va bu debugger ni o‘chirib qo‘yadi.

00:01:13.390 --> 00:01:17.060
Keyin ilova odatdagidek ishlaydi, 
tugmani bosganim zahoti 

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:17.770
darhol ekranni yangilaydi.

